00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,727
When Failure Became My Teacher

2
00:00:03,727 --> 00:00:07,882
There was a time in my life when I thought

3
00:00:07,882 --> 00:00:13,991
success was a straight path, a road paved with certainty

4
00:00:13,991 --> 00:00:16,956
and easy victories

5
00:00:16,956 --> 00:00:23,550
I imagined that hard work alone would guarantee results, that

6
00:00:23,550 --> 00:00:27,147
effort would always meet reward

7
00:00:27,147 --> 00:00:32,818
But life, as I learned, has a way of humbling

8
00:00:32,818 --> 00:00:36,656
even the most determined hearts

9
00:00:36,656 --> 00:00:43,683
My first major failure arrived silently, almost without warning

10
00:00:43,683 --> 00:00:49,439
I had poured months brace it, listen to it, and

11
00:00:49,439 --> 00:00:53,889
allow it to guide you toward the person you are

12
00:00:53,889 --> 00:00:56,363
meant to become

